name: Georgia State University - 55 Park Place Building, 5th Floor (School of Social Work)
directions: Go through the lobby, take the elevators on the right to the 5th floor. When exiting the elevator area, turn to the right & look for the School of Social Work front desk. State at the front desk that you would like to use the single-stall restroom and ask for directions to that restroom. (You'll end up walking to the left, down the hall, and the bathroom will be on the right, across from office 557.)
comment: You will need to flash your Georgia State University ID at the security desk in the lobby (they are checking that you are GSU-affiliated). Those who are not GSU students, staff, or faculty may need to sign-in at the security desk in order to be granted access to the elevators.
